title: For Sale:  1996 Buell Thunderbolt S2
postcontent: Very rare survivor, 100% original, 1996 Buell S2 Thunderbolt (mid 1995 production date). Last of the hand built Buell's. Harley Davidson 1203cc free breathing engine. Hand laid fiberglass body work that was meticulously factory painted with numerous layers of paints, giving it a color changing effect (this one is the rare blue/purple/black dependent on lighting). Hand tig welded frame built by an expert Nascar race car builder hired by Eric Buell. These bikes were built to go road racing right off the showroom floor, and cost more than most of the new Harley's they sold beside. This bike was completely gone through last fall with all new (nos) Buell and Harley Davidson parts: clutch and cable, throttle cables, Harley battery, new seals & gaskets, new brake lines & brake pads, calipers were rebuilt with new seals, new Michelin Pilot Pro rear tire & Pilot Pro 3 front tire, new Buell rider foot pegs, all bulbs, plugs, Screamin' Eagle plug wires, upgraded billet racing air cleaner/ head breather backing plate, White Bro.s racing muffler, wheel bearings, steering stabilizer, K&N air filter and more. Hidden underbody purple lights w/ hidden switch. It didn't really need anything, but was redone for the sake of reliabilty. Turnkey ready for the season. 2 new security keys, service manual, front and rear racing jack stands, extra new and used parts included. Passes inspection 100%. Have all take off parts (grips, pegs, etc. except factory muffler). These are the only Buell's that are collectible and becoming more valuable. Some items mentioned are not in pic's, I havn't taken new ones since adding the front tire, pegs, or changing the grips and pipe wrap to black. If it's listed, it's available. Don't ask. I don't respond to spam. I despise con men/scammers/spammers and people who don't read an ad before responding. Lowered price while I'm on vacation. Great deal. Once I go back to work, I won't care if I just keep it. Had it out for a nice ride today 6/21/17. Running perfect. $2500 b.0.
